These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There 2 different types of food: watermelon, grapefruit
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, bird
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, surfing
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
2. the person eating grapefruit is in an even position##4
3. the owner of the bird is the person eating watermelon##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Food      | watermelon  | grapefruit   |
| Pet   | bird     | chinchilla   |
| Sport         | surfing | cycling |
| Transport     | jet-ski | taxi    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: american, australian
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, documentary
The people have 2 different jobs:  dressmaker, scientist
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, tram
1. the scientist is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching action movies is the person driving the tram##1
3. the australian is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Nationality          | american     | australian |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | action  |
| Job           | scientist         | dressmaker     |
| Transport     | motorbike   | tram    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, lily
2 different pets are kept: frog, lizard
2 different games are played: billiard, scrabble
1. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
2. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person who growslily##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | soy-milk     | hot-chocolate |
| Flower         | lily | balloon-flower    |
| Pet         | frog         | lizard        |
| Game   | billiard         | scrabble    |

 #################################

 
