1. the fan of classical is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3
3. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Food    | lettuce | strawberry    |
| Music-Genre         | classical        | folk |
| Pet         | frog          | goat     |
| Transport   | roller        | tram     |

 